  "name": "Lingering Breath [Mythic]",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/skills/ice_11.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The creature can expend one use of <a class=\"entity-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; background-image: none; background-color: initial; padding: 0px; color: #ff6400; border: none;\" draggable=\"false\" data-pack=\"pf-content.pf-universal-monster-rules\" data-id=\"emNdW1Y7gFdGwNpo\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; text-decoration-line: underline;\">mythic power</span></a> as a free action when it uses its <a class=\"entity-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; background-image: none; background-color: initial; padding: 0px; color: #ff6400; border: none;\" draggable=\"false\" data-pack=\"pf-content.pf-universal-monster-rules\" data-id=\"pQMisEKPQrTWyLh0\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; text-decoration-line: underline;\">breath weapon</span></a> to make the area radiate energy damage (of the same type as the breath weapon) for 1 round per mythic rank. Any creature in, entering, or passing through the breath weapon&rsquo;s area during this duration takes damage according to the creature&rsquo;s size. This ability has no effect on breath weapons that do not deal energy damage.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Table 3-1: Lingering Breath Damage</h2>\n<table class=\"inner\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th><strong>Creature Size</strong></th>\n<th><strong>Points of Energy Damage</strong></th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Medium or smaller</td>\n<td>2d4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Large</td>\n<td>2d6</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Huge</td>\n<td>2d8</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Gargantuan</td>\n<td>4d6</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Colossal</td>\n<td>4d8</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em>Format</em>: lingering breath (2d6 fire, 5 rounds)</p>\n<p><em>Location</em>: Special Attacks.</p>",
